headline.main: Court Meets on Ukraine Tax Chief's $74M Embezzlement Case
headline.print_headline: Court Meets on Ukraine Tax Chief's $74M Embezzlement Case

lead_paragraph: A court in Kiev was hearing motions Monday on the $74 million embezzlement case against Ukraine's top tax official.
